{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, AI-enabled near-field ISAC is a promising research direction.",
    "AI-enabled secure ISACDue to the inherent spectrum sharing and openness of the wireless environment, ISAC faces a unique security challenge [268,269].",
    "The dual-function signal containing the confidential message is vulnerable to eavesdropping, especially if the target is a potential eavesdropper.",
    "In particular, the ISAC-BS prefers to direct its beam to the interested target, which increases the risk of information leakage [270].",
    "To deal with this problem, researchers tend to pay attention to the secure ISAC, which takes transmission security into consideration when designing the transmission scheme."
  ]
}